title: Springer Lab Manuals [Updated at 2016.03.18]
description: Springer Lab Manuals are useful and practical tools for anyone working at the lab bench. They are designed with you, the practitioner, in mind. If you have little or no experience with a particular technique or if you are familiar with the technique but want to keep up to date on recent developments, Springer Lab Manuals can guide you along the way. As well as practising professionals, postgraduate and postdoctoral research scientists and laboratory technicians working in various areas of biomedical and biological science will also find the Springer Lab Manuals practical and easy to use
